Try the maze yourself: https://reeborg.ca/reeborg.html?lang=en&mode=python&menu=worlds%2Fmenus%2Freeborg_intro_en.json&name=Maze&url=worlds%2Ftutorial_en%2Fmaze1.json

Functions used:
- define a new function
- while loop
- el/else within while loop


def right():
    turn_left()
    turn_left()
    turn_left()
    
def move_towards():
    if wall_on_right():
        if front_is_clear():
            move()
        else:
            turn_left()
    else:
        right()
        move()
        
while at_goal() != True:
    move_towards()
# != is not true
